  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个智能灌溉系统的状态流转图。系统启动后应该先等待灌溉时段，这个状态叫\"EsperandoFranjaHoraria\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "EsperandoFranjaHoraria"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点直接连到等待时段状态。那进入灌溉时段后呢？需要读取传感器数据吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EsperandoFranjaHoraria",
        "LeyendoSensores"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，时段到了就进入\"LeyendoSensores\"读取温湿度等数据，然后流转到\"EvaluandoCondiciones\"评估是否满足灌溉条件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LeyendoSensores",
        "EvaluandoCondiciones"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加这两个状态和流转。评估条件这里需要分支吗？比如温度不合适的情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EvaluandoCondiciones",
        "EsperandoTemperatura"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要分支。如果\"Temperatura no adecuada\"就进入\"EsperandoTemperatura\"等待，温度合适了再返回重新评估。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EvaluandoCondiciones",
        "EsperandoTemperatura"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，温度等待状态形成了循环。那评估通过后的主流程呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EvaluandoCondiciones",
        "Regando",
        "SistemaInactivo"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "分两种情况：如果\"No hay zonas para regar\"没有可灌溉区域，进入\"SistemaInactivo\"休眠，等待下个周期再回到时段等待。如果有区域需要灌溉，进入\"Regando\"状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EvaluandoCondiciones",
        "SistemaInactivo",
        "Regando",
        "EsperandoFranjaHoraria"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加这两个分支。灌溉状态后面是启动水泵吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Regando",
        "BombaActiva"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，\"Regando\"之后\"Iniciar riego\"进入\"BombaActiva\"，然后\"Activar aspersores por zona\"激活\"AspersoresActivos\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Regando",
        "BombaActiva",
        "AspersoresActivos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "喷灌激活后需要循环处理多个区域吧？完成后的结束流程呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AspersoresActivos",
        "EvaluandoCondiciones",
        "ApagandoSistema"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，\"Repetir por zona\"返回\"EvaluandoCondiciones\"继续处理其他区域。所有区域完成后\"Finalizar riego\"进入\"ApagandoSistema\"，最后回到\"EsperandoFranjaHoraria\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AspersoresActivos",
        "EvaluandoCondiciones",
        "ApagandoSistema",
        "EsperandoFranjaHoraria"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "整个流程闭环了。我确认一下：系统从启动等待时段开始，读取传感器评估条件，根据温度和区域需求决定休眠或灌溉，灌溉时依次启动水泵和喷灌器，支持多区域循环，最后关闭系统回到等待状态。对吗？",
